text: "Strut" is a 1984 song by Scottish singer Sheena Easton. It was taken from her fifth studio album A Private Heaven. It went to number 7 in the United States and Canada, number 8 in New Zealand, number 21 in Germany, number 18 in South Africa and number 13 in Australia. It did not chart in the United Kingdom. It was nominated for a Grammy Award in 1985. == References == Category:1984 songs Category:Sheena Easton songs Category:Dance-pop songs Category:Synth-pop songs
